# AI Doctor (Book 04)

Full manual: `docs/foundation/04-ai-behaviour/`

## Pipeline

- Entry: `runIntelligenceEngine` in `packages/ai/src/intelligence-engine.ts`
- Vision when image present; respect `VISION_MIN_CONFIDENCE` gates
- Answers: short-first sections via `answer-formatter.ts` — not walls of text
- Evidence: `buildEvidenceCards` with correct `language` — never `String(object)` in UI

## Language

- Lock conversation language (`tr` | `en`); no mixed languages in one session
- Evidence card titles and upload errors must be localized

## Safety

- Never claim certainty; use "most likely", confidence %, "what to check next"
- No automatic pesticide/chemical dosages; disclaimers on treatment guidance
- Photo-only: ask clarifying questions; do not invent crop/species without vision support
